{
  "stem": "4184.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there was a young nun there, and she already wore her black outfit, which means she's been there for now a few years.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because you get five years for final vows.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she fascinated me, this one nun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And one day, I-- her room was behind my bunk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I saw her combing her hair.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And you're not supposed to have long hair under your outfit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the next day I asked her-- I says, you have long hair under there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You're not supposed to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she says, oh, it's nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She kind of pushed aside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Now the day of liberation arrives, and we were all looking out of the window.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the soldiers, the Americans, came through our town and were marching, and everybody's excited.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she is so excited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She looks out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She made a remark-- oh, look, isn't that a handsome soldier?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So finally, I thought, no, she's not for real.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Within about a week, she got a letter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I saw her running through my dorm trying to go into her room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I says, Mother, you're so happy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You have good news?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She says, yeah, my cousin survived the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a soldier.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, Mother, your cousin, or was it your husband, maybe, or your boyfriend or something?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then she told me that she was Jewish from Belgium, and she had made a pact with her fiancee that she would be able to go to France [INAUDIBLE], she would become a nun, never thinking the war would last five or more years.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when he would come back, he would find her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's exactly what she did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he found her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but I can picture her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was a beautiful women.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just a beautiful woman.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
